# {{SERVICE_NAME}}

.NET 8 microservice scaffolded from `scaffold-csharp-microservice`.

## Layout

```
src/
  Service/          ASP.NET Core minimal-API host (Program.cs, Endpoints/, Models/, Validators/, Middleware/, Extensions/)
  Application/      MediatR commands, queries, handlers, application services
  Domain/           Entities, repository interfaces + Mongo implementations
  Infrastructure/   IRepository + BaseRepository<T> (generic Mongo CRUD)
tests/
  UnitTests/        xUnit + Moq + FluentAssertions
  IntegrationTests/ xUnit + EphemeralMongo + WebApplicationFactory
```

## Prerequisites

- .NET 8 SDK
- MongoDB (locally via `brew services start mongodb-community@8.0` or Docker)

## Run

```bash
dotnet run --project src/Service
```

Swagger UI: <http://localhost:5070/swagger>
Prometheus metrics: <http://localhost:5070/metrics>

## Test

```bash
dotnet test
```

Integration tests use `EphemeralMongo`, so no MongoDB instance is required to run them.

## Build container

```bash
docker build -f src/Service/Dockerfile -t {{SERVICE_NAME_KEBAB}}:latest .
```
